A Ladysmith 5 SAI soldier has been brutally stabbed to death, this evening, 27 September 2016 at the Lions Park, along Soldier&#8217;s Way.It is reported that the soldier was in the company of a woman, at the local park. It is reported that the woman was raped.The details of the attack are not clear and police are on scene gathering much needed evidence. Updates to follow&nbsp;